OL,3,CAmazon workers in Coventry narrowly
OL,4,Creject union in ballot
OL,6,FA ballot of staff at Amazon's Coventry
OL,7,Fsite for union recognition has failed
OL,8,Fto reach a majority.
OL,10,FThe GMB union said workers at the
OL,11,Fonline giant's Coventry site voted by
OL,12,F49.5% in favour of union recognition,
OL,13,Ffalling just short of a majority.
OL,15,FThe union had called the vote
OL,16,F"historic and legally binding" as it
OL,17,Fwould have been the first time the
OL,18,Fonline retail giant had recognised a
OL,19,Funion in the UK.
