OL,4,Creject union in ballot
OL,6,FMore than 3,000 workers at Amazon's
OL,7,FCoventry fulfilment centre were asked
OL,8,Fif they would like to be represented
OL,9,Fby a union in a ballot that ran from 8
OL,10,Fto 12 July.
OL,12,FThe vote, overseen by the government's
OL,13,FCentral Arbitration Committee, could
OL,14,Fhave meant Amazon needed to recognise
OL,15,Fa trade union and negotiate pay, terms
OL,16,Fand conditions.
