OL,6,FGMB official Stuart Richards said:
OL,7,F"Amazon now faces a legal challenge,
OL,8,Fwhile the fire lit by workers in
OL,9,FCoventry and across the UK is still
OL,10,Fburning.
OL,12,F"GMB will carry on the fight for the
OL,13,Fpay and recognition they deserve."
OL,15,FAn Amazon spokesperson said: "We want
OL,16,Fto thank everyone who voted in this
OL,17,Fballot.
